<P>
   DIAL-AROUND (Undated) -- 10-10 ``dial-around'' services are
stirring the long-distance phone market. Whether you really save
money using them depends on your calling patterns. By Ronald
Rosenberg. 1700 words. (2 takes; includes 10-10 comparison text
table.)
