<P>
   VENTURE-FUNDS (Boston) -- As US stock markets nosedived last
summer and most investors bit their nails, venture capital funds
pumped a record-setting $550.8 million into 114 young New England
companies. By Jerry Ackerman. 1400 words. PHOTO
</P>
