<DOCNO> NYT19981118.0096 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-11-18 13:29 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6613 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u d &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FOOD-THANKSVIGING-2TA     11-18 1118
