   FOOD-TURKEY-AUTHOR (Undated) Rick Rodgers approaches
Thanksgiving as if he were Eisenhower organizing the Allied
invasion of Europe. That means planning, planning and more
planning. And why not? Thanksgiving can be the home cook's version
of ``The Longest Day.''
</P>
<P>
   By Gregory Roberts. (story will move in the ``d'' category)
