Edwards, a 71-year-old preacher, consists of a 54-acre compound _
several plain wooden buildings, three mobile homes and several
sheds, all laid out against a utilitarian backdrop of rusty
earthmoving equipment. (Konigsmark, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
