   Other Mets as needed.
</P>
<P>
   BBA-YANKS (New York) _ The latest on Bernie Williams, Albert
Belle, Brian Jordan. By Buster Olney.
</P>
<P>
   FBN-EWBANK (Undated) _ Former New York Jets and Baltimore Colts
players talk about Weeb Ewbank, who coached both teams to N.F.L.
championships and who died on Tuesday at the age of 91. By Frank
Litsky.
</P>
<P>
   TEN-CHASE (New York) _ Women's tennis action at the Chase
Championships. By Robin Finn.
</P>
