<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-11-18 15:36 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6940 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SPCL-MENTAL-RESEARCH-     11-18 1345
