</P>
<P>
   COMDEX _ LAS VEGAS _ Michael Dell and his key lieutenants
entertained the press at the Las Vegas Country Club. Dell eschewed
the overpopulated roster of keynoters in favor of the the country
club. Plus, other hot stuff from the floor. (Mahoney, Austin
American-Statesman).
</P>
