   FBC-BIGGAMES _ The results of several games this weekend could
ultimately decide the teams that will play in the Fiesta Bowl for
the national championship. Top-ranked Tennessee faces a difficult
challenege against Kentucky, No. 2 Kansas State plays at No. 19
Missouri and No. 3 UCLA meets rival USC. No. 4 Florida and No. 5
Florida State also meet, with the winner hoping to move into the
national championship picture with losses by higher-ranked teams.
Also, Arkansas travels to Mississippi State in a game that could
decide the SEC West champion. (Barnhart, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 20.
