<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-MIDEAST-ECON-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   MIDEAST-ECON (Undated) will not move in tonight's New York Times
News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Nov. 18. &QL;
