other violations kills four children under age 4. By Mitchell
Zuckoff. 1200 words.
</P>
<P>
   PATRIOTS-STADIUM (Boston) -- The New England Patriots appear
ready to accept an offer to move to Hartford, Conn. in return for a
new $280 million stadium that would be paid for by taxpayers,
bondholders, and football fans. By Tina Cassidy. 1300 words. (a and
s coding)
</P>
<P>
   METEOR-WHOOPS (Undated) -- Thanks to incorrect predictions, most
scientists hoping for a close look at the Leonid meteor storm were
in the wrong place. The best viewing was probably in the
mid-Atlantic. By David L. Chandler. 800 words.
</P>
