   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   MA-TAXATION (Boston) -- Despite progress in reducing overall
property tax rates that were once among the highest in the nation,
Massachusetts businesses shoulder an increasingly greater share of
the reduced burden, industry report says. By Lynnley Browning. 500
words.
</P>
<P>
   MA-RETAIL (Boston) -- With unemployment at its lowest level in
decades, retailers can't remember a holiday season when it has been
more difficult to find sales clerks to handle the rush of shoppers.
By Kimberly Blanton and Judy Rakowsky. 1000 words.
