<HEADLINE>
REPUBLICAN LEADERSHIP SELECTS FIRST AFRICAN AMERICAN 
</HEADLINE>
   (EDs: CHANGES word in lede from claim to show)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service Clients.)  
 By JUDY HOLLAND  
 c.1998 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ Rep. J.C. Watts, a former University of Oklahoma
