   INSIDE STORIES PROMOTED ON PAGE 1:
</P>
<P>
   BISHOPS-ABORTION (Washington) _ In a pointed statement that
calls Roman Catholic politicians to heed the teachings of their
faith, the nation's Catholic bishops declared they had a pastoral
responsibility to speak out to public officials who support
abortion rights and euthanasia and urge them ``to a change of
heart.'' By Gustav Niebuhr.
</P>
