<P>
   BKW-REIGN (Seattle) Val Whiting _ not Shalonda Enis, not Kate
Starbird _ has been the Reign's big gun so far, with double-doubles
in each game of the team's 3-0 start. Featurized advance for Reign
hosting two-time league champion Columbus.
</P>
<P>
   By Jim Street. (story will move in the ``s'' category)
