<HEADLINE>
DEAL TO BRING PATRIOTS TO HARTFORD SAID `REAL CLOSE' 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (a and s coding)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By TINA CASSIDY  
 c.1998 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   BOSTON _ The state of Connecticut is trying to lure the New
