<P>
   BC-MICROSOFT-SUN-NYT (moved on Tuesday, Nov. 17)
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Tuesday, Nov. 17,
about a Federal court order that stops Microsoft from shipping its
own version of Sun Microsystems' Java programming language
misstated the year the companies signed a licensing agreement at
issue in their dispute. It was March 1996, not 1995.
