<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-11-18 22:21 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8035 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FBN-PATRIOTS-BOS &LR;      11-18 1308
